data.description: Price reduced for quick sale! Perfect for families, this Attached Single Family home Features 3 bedrooms , 2.5 bathrooms 1 car garage. Has a newer kitchen with granite counter tops and brand new S&S Appliances. First floor has all tile throughout , Upstairs Floors & stairway are bamboo wood floors. Roof done in 2013. Water heater installed in 2021. Master Bedroom is upstairs with updated master bath guest bath and 2 room upstairs as well , 1 full bedroom downstairs with half bath. Home has an amazing fenced backyard yard with room for a pool. Located In the heart of Coral Springs, close to highways, restaurants, and shopping malls. Please contact the agent to schedule a tour.
